        <Parent_String>whaling vessels [300232758], hunting and commercial fishing vessels [300232732], watercraft by function [300232728], watercraft by specific type [300219289], watercraft [300042940], vehicles (transportation) [300219258], Transportation Vehicles (hierarchy name) [300042929], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
